[SN]TITLE[SN]
Michael Sheen: 'Frightening time' for Port Talbot

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
Welsh actor Michael Sheen has called the job cuts in the steel industry in Port Talbot "frightening for the town".

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
19 January 2016 Last updated at 10:38 GMT
More than 1,000 jobs are being cut at Tata Steel, the majority at the Port Talbot plant in south Wales.
Michael Sheen grew up in the Port Talbot area and has made a film set there. He spoke to BBC Newnsight's Emily Maitlis.
